abstract: Baseball Roundup; Texas Rangers defeat Oakland Athletics, 8-1; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Rangers moved a season-high 14 games over .500 and extended their lead to three and a half games over the idle Astros in the American League West.

headline.main: Rangers Extend Lead Over Astros in the A.L. West
